          <updateDate>2018-03-15T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>This bill prohibits the Department of Veterans Affairs from requiring a veteran's surviving spouse to return payments of dependent's compensation or of a pension as a married veteran for the month in which the veteran dies.</p>]]></text>
